  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: if you send transaction request with amount less than  0.000001 from wallet, it is displayed  with an exponential notation in chat.\r\nNot reproducible if you send transaction request from chat with same amount.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n0.0000002\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n2e-7\r\n![exp](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/42888418-ea702942-8ab0-11e8-8610-2516fd095d27.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Wallet\r\n- Tap on \"Receive transaction\" -> Send transaction request\r\n- Specify amount < 0.000001 (i.e. 0.0000002)\r\n- Tap on Send request\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: release 61 (0.9.23 (6212))\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n* TF session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8528574/sessions/4396611705/?accessToken=AqNKb4GRL8qcUO4AWycIA2nplKQ\r\n\r\n\r\n",
